{"tid":759160,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文慎入]仆街眼鏡鋪 整爛左唔認數","createTime":"2018-07-28T11:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T15:13:44.000Z","uid":12896,"like":5,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"720677c4d1ef794722ddb4a8e86d1beffcc198c0","tid":759160,"uid":12896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T11:01:19.000Z","msg":"旺角 法國眼鏡店<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.yp.com.hk/23887606/373805/ch/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.yp.com.hk%2F23887606%2F373805%2Fch%2F&d=d8xljKYk2UWvEYkcFoS%2F17%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=5d1502d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.yp.com.hk/23887606/373805/ch/</a><br />\n<br />\n認住呢間仆街舖頭，唔好中伏！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/185524_e0877ec52345dda834da06dc21c09646.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F185524_e0877ec52345dda834da06dc21c09646.png&h=2af1c527&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢間嘢幫襯過幾次，感覺還好，點知今日就中撚曬伏！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日幫人拎兩副眼鏡架去配鏡片，由於佢本人唔得閒，就拎佢戴緊個副眼鏡去參考度數。<br />\n（佢本人個朝仲戴緊，然後放入眼鏡盒俾我，檢查過眼鏡完整無缺，我亦都有俾同行嘅人睇過冇事。）<br />\n<br />\n我去到舖頭，放左三個眼鏡盒出黎，睇舖嘅係個女人，一個八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我同佢講要配兩副鏡片，然後我拎舊果副出黎遞埋比佢，佢仲話：「咁成熟，唔係你㗎啦。」我隨口答左佢係。心諗關你撚事咩，整你就整啦<br />\n<br />\n說時遲那時快，啪一聲，我望住佢，佢望撚住我，眼鏡係佢手上面，個架斷左！然後佢就話：「我細細力咋，唔係我整㗎，你都見到我輕輕力㗎......」bilibala講左一大堆推卸責任嘅嘢。佢老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 擺撚明係佢手上先爛，唔通我識念力？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我同佢講副眼鏡不嬲都好地地點會無啦啦爛，佢又重複一大堆個d嘢，最仆街嘅係隔離有個廢老（客）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又加把嘴話呢d金屬疲勞。關你撚事咩廢老，副野唔係你實咁講架啦，換著係佢，實係度屌9人啦，死廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我個陣好嬲，但係唔想爆9佢，因為佢都唔撚會認，我就打比眼鏡主人，佢就認為呢個女人講到底都唔會認唔會賠，勁無賴，所以同佢拗都冇9用。收線之後，條八婆又講：「我好細力，冇可能整爛，可以解釋到」<br />\n<br />\n然後我屌9左條八婆幾句就帶曬啲嘢走人。但係其實真係好唔忿氣，無啦啦比條八婆整爛副眼鏡，仲要唔認數，條友真係超級無賴。<br />\n<br />\n我打咁長文擺上黎，只係唔想咁多位巴打絲打中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce49e0cdf6c29efdae113f68c9081ac5a0292b7","tid":759160,"uid":37918,"like":67,"dislike":2,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T11:06:25.000Z","msg":"忍唔住笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個刻怕事走人 轉個攞鍵盤打千字文發洩"},{"pid":"aa523e050773862a2d73242a76e2bdbe419603d7","tid":759160,"uid":121130,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T11:08:45.000Z","msg":"行規客架同客講 整爛唔負責 講左先整<br />\n真係爛既熟客碼返住個客就比公司平平地既架送比佢<br />\n二樣都唔識 正廢柴"},{"pid":"c2bdef744edad44b7d6b45da84c65d9cdd8f7d1f","tid":759160,"uid":141007,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T11:13:59.000Z","msg":"黑店 推到佢仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7e79455dd5d4c968c3a1cca1fd1f120f43a187","tid":759160,"uid":30006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T11:18:20.000Z","msg":"呢間野配左好左年，老板幾好人"},{"pid":"c3e9616af0f31f8b37108920bed6fa1991909e89","tid":759160,"uid":20725,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T11:19:28.000Z","msg":"樓豬好廢 比人恰完要上網post文"},{"pid":"7bff63f9a706353f492f55c50439cd749052b775","tid":759160,"uid":37203,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T11:20:03.000Z","msg":"又係走住黎屌，抵你俾人恰啦"},{"pid":"9e849bd425ede17700049e7d0644dda7f32ab1a2","tid":759160,"uid":18411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T11:21:43.000Z","msg":"陰公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廢極都識報警掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6bde6ee46be142eb5f93bc56ba3baf2781fb61","tid":759160,"uid":99700,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T11:21:46.000Z","msg":"呢D係金屬疲勞